flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>ٱلۡهُدَىٰ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> فَأَخَذَتۡهُمۡ صَٰعِقَةُ <a data-content='المهين' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>ٱلۡعَذَابِ ٱلۡهُونِ</a> بِمَا كَانُواْ </div><div>يَكۡسِبُونَ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>١٧</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> وَنَجَّيۡنَا ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُواْ وَكَانُواْ يَتَّقُونَ ١٨ وَيَوۡمَ يُحۡشَرُ أَعۡدَآءُ </div><div>ٱللَّهِ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>إِلَى</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> ٱلنَّارِ <a data-content='يُـحـْـبَـسُ سَوَابقهم ليلحقهم تواليهم' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>فَهُمۡ يُوزَعُونَ</a> ١٩ حَتَّىٰٓ إِذَا مَا جَآءُوهَا شَهِدَ </div><div>عَلَيۡهِمۡ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>سَمۡعُهُمۡ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> وَأَبۡصَٰرُهُمۡ وَجُلُودُهُم بِمَا كَانُواْ يَعۡمَلُونَ </div><div>٢٠</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'></div>",
